Package: ecooracle
Title: Bootstrap EcoOracle Support for R Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Brad", "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a small R helper for onboarding R packages into the
    EcoOracle ecosystem. The package exposes use_ecooracle(), which wraps the
    canonical bootstrap script to scaffold '.ecosystem.yml', workflow files,
    and EcoAtlas tools into a package repository.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements: bash

